<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Spiral_Dance" title="The Spiral Dance">The Spiral Dance</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Starhawk" title="Starhawk">Starhawk</a></li>
<li><i>Staying Alive: Women, Ecology and Development</i> by <a href="/wiki/Vandana_Shiva" title="Vandana Shiva">Vandana Shiva</a></li>
<li><i>Thinking Green! Essays on Environmentalism, Feminism, and Nonviolence,</i> by <a href="/wiki/Petra_Kelly" title="Petra Kelly">Petra Kelly</a></li>
<li><i>Tomorrow's Biodiversity</i> by <a href="/wiki/Vandana_Shiva" title="Vandana Shiva">Vandana Shiva</a></li>
<li><i>Woman and Nature: The Roaring Inside Her</i>, by <a href="/wiki/Susan_Griffin" title="Susan Griffin">Susan Griffin</a></li>
</ul>
<dl>
<dt>Fiction</dt>
</dl>
