<li><i><a href="/wiki/Buffalo_Gals,_Won%27t_You_Come_Out_Tonight" title="Buffalo Gals, Won't You Come Out Tonight">Buffalo Gals, Won't You Come Out Tonight</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Ursula_K._Le_Guin" title="Ursula K. Le Guin">Ursula K. Le Guin</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Fifth_Sacred_Thing" title="The Fifth Sacred Thing">The Fifth Sacred Thing</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Starhawk" title="Starhawk">Starhawk</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Gate_to_Women%27s_Country" title="The Gate to Women's Country">The Gate to Women's Country</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Sheri_S._Tepper" title="Sheri S. Tepper">Sheri S. Tepper</a></li>
<li><i>The Holdfast Chronicles</i> by <a href="/wiki/Suzy_McKee_Charnas" title="Suzy McKee Charnas">Suzy McKee Charnas</a></li>
<li><i>Native Tongue</i> by <a href="/wiki/Suzette_Haden_Elgin" title="Suzette Haden Elgin">Suzette Haden Elgin</a></li>
