<li><i>Prodigal Summer</i> by <a href="/wiki/Barbara_Kingsolver" title="Barbara Kingsolver">Barbara Kingsolver</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Surfacing_(novel)" title="Surfacing (novel)">Surfacing</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Margaret_Atwood" title="Margaret Atwood">Margaret Atwood</a></li>
