<li><i><a href="/wiki/Woman_on_the_Edge_of_Time" title="Woman on the Edge of Time">Woman on the Edge of Time</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Marge_Piercy" title="Marge Piercy">Marge Piercy</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Kin_of_Ata_are_Waiting_for_You" title="The Kin of Ata are Waiting for You">The Kin of Ata are Waiting for You</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Dorothy_Bryant" title="Dorothy Bryant">Dorothy Bryant</a></li>
