<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Temple_of_My_Familiar" title="The Temple of My Familiar">The Temple of My Familiar</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Alice_Walker" title="Alice Walker">Alice Walker</a></li>
</ul>
